@startuml SecHack365-Fans_PyJailBreak

actor User
participant "Next.js Server" as NextJS
participant "React Components" as React
participant "Redux Store" as Redux
participant "API Client" as APIClient
participant "Backend API" as Backend

User -> NextJS : Access website
activate NextJS
NextJS -> React : Render components
activate React

User -> React : Configure scan
React -> Redux : Update configuration
activate Redux

User -> React : Manage payloads
React -> Redux : Update payloads

User -> React : Execute scan
React -> Redux : Get configuration and payloads
Redux --> React : Configuration and payloads
React -> APIClient : Execute scan request
activate APIClient
APIClient -> Backend : Send scan request
activate Backend
Backend --> APIClient : Return scan results
deactivate Backend
APIClient --> React : Return results
deactivate APIClient
React -> Redux : Update scan results
Redux --> React : Updated state
React --> User : Display results
deactivate Redux
deactivate React

User -> NextJS : Access API documentation
NextJS -> React : Render Swagger UI
React --> User : Display API docs

@enduml